Acceptance: P19 action intents, previews, confirmations, and dispatch envelopes retain the initiating immutable Actor snapshot and logical Principal/account lineage, then re-resolve current authority at execution. Actor, link, account, target, or policy changes invalidate confirmation; no Room history or another participant can supply identity. Jobs, receipts, and webhooks are separate slices. Canonical contract: docs/plans/2026-07-13-github-user-attribution-and-feature-discovery.md.